    {
        id: uuidv4(),
        url: fries,
        item: "Papas fritas",
        price: 7,
        tag: "foo"
    },
    {
        id: uuidv4(),
        url: onionRings,
        item: "Aros de cebolla",
        price: 7,
        tag: "food"
    }
]

export default foodData
